&lt;p&gt;This was a bizarre day trip. I will talk about it someday. For now, I&amp;rsquo;ll just enjoy the views.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Big Sur</title><link>https://www.nonpunctual.org/places/big-sur/</link><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.nonpunctual.org/places/big-sur/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;
