&lt;p&gt;I was on a work trip for Fleet in SF &amp;amp; decided to take a few days to drive up &amp;amp; down the coast, going as far south as I could through Big Sur. I want to go back &amp;amp; spend a full week or 2 in the area. It looks &amp;amp; feels like a different planet to me.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>San Jose</title><link>https://www.nonpunctual.org/places/san-jose/</link><pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2017 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.nonpunctual.org/places/san-jose/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;
